    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Tin tức & Mẹo chăm sóc thú cưng</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="blog-card bg-white rounded-lg shadow p-4">
                <img src="https://file.hstatic.net/200000101597/article/poodle_309752cab9084d97ae9566ec39994291_large.png" alt="Blog" class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-md mb-4">
